articles.title: 8.8 magnitude quake strikes off Russia's Far East
articles.description: One of the strongest earthquakes ever recorded has hit off Russia's sparsely populated Far East, sending tsunami waves into Japan, Hawaii and the U.S. West Coast [2, 3, 4].

articles.title: Gunman who killed 4 at NYC building was targeting NFL offices, but took wrong elevator, mayor says
articles.description: A gunman killed 4 people at an office building in NYC, and officials are working to determine the motive. The mayor stated that the gunman was targeting NFL offices but took the wrong elevator [2, 3, 4].
